COMPILATION:
premake4 gmake
make
./A5 Assets/$FILE.lua

INSTRUCTION:
- BOUNDING_BOX is disabled by default
- EXTRA FEATURE:
  - I implemented texture mapping for spheres, cubes and planes, it can be
    found in my unique scene
  - Unique Scene: unique_scene.lua. I have also attached a png file of the
    unique scene in the Assets folder, which has a name of unique_scene.png
    - The scene is about a farm in a dry land. There is a meteor in the center
      of the scene.
- Bounding Box:
  - I used rectangles to make bounding box.
- Resolution:
  - I changed all resolutions to 1024
- Outputs: 
  - nonhier2.lua outputs nonhier2.png
  - nonhier.lua outputs nonhier-bb.png
  - macho-cows outputs macho-cows-bb.png
- Sample images in the Assets folder are:
  - unique_scene.png
  - simple.png
  - simple-cows.png
  - macho-cows.png
  - macho-cows-bb.png
  - real-macho-cows-newview.png
  - hier.png
  - nonhier.png
  - nonhier-bb.png
  - nonhier2.png
